sub_title: Looking forward to a new experience
summary:
Most of my experiences are working in the administrative rolls within different segments such as commerce and the oil and gas industry. Moving to another country and facing completely new challenges in life (like learning a new language) also brought me different challenges work wise as learning other skills and different professional approaches from a different culture than my own. 
But no matter the challenges are I will always face them the best way I can and always get the best lessons out of the situations. No matter the new roles and the jobs I get I will always commit myself into accomplishing the best work I can do for the company and for the team.
